== Overview ==
The Ion V2 is a modified base version [[Ion|Ion reactor]].
It was designed to enhance the power reserve, and manages to do so well.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Ion V2 Reactor can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.

